{"format": "tiptap/v1", "updatedAt": "2026-06-22T06:57:16.113Z", "doc": {"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Init Pitfalls"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (initialization pitfalls) are common mistakes in weight initialization that cause neural networks to fail training, converge slowly, or learn nothing at all. These errors are especially critical because they happen "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "before training starts"}, {"type": "text", "text": " and can make deep networks un-trainable from the first iteration."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,", "alt": "Init Pitfalls — concept overview"}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The 4 Major Initialization Pitfalls"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Pitfall 1: ❌ Zero Initialization"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "What"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Setting all weights to zero ("}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "W = 0"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ")"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "What happens"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":\n- Every neuron outputs 0 in the forward pass\n- Gradients become 0 during backpropagation\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "No weight updates occur → no learning happens"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Why it's catastrophic"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":\n- All neurons receive "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "identical gradients"}, {"type": "text", "text": "\n- All weights update identically → "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "symmetry never breaks"}, {"type": "text", "text": "\n- Network behaves like "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "a single neuron"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (linear model)"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# BAD - Never do this\nW = np.zeros((100, 128))  # All zeros!"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Result"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Network is a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "linear model"}, {"type": "text", "text": " that can't capture non-linear relationships."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Pitfall 2: ❌ Constant Non-Zero Initialization"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "What"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Setting all weights to the same constant (e.g., 0.5)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "What happens"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":\n- All neurons start identical (same output)\n- Gradients are identical for all neurons\n- Updates happen identically → "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "neurons never diversify"}, {"type": "text", "text": ".md)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Why it's bad"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":\n- Same problem as zero initialization (symmetry)\n- Network becomes a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "single neuron"}, {"type": "text", "text": " despite having hundreds\n- Acts like a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "linear model"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", can't learn non-linear patterns"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# BAD - Never do this\nW = np.ones((100, 128)) * 0.5  # All same value!"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Result"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Network fails to learn diverse features from data..md)"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Pitfall 3: ❌ Very Small Random Values"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "What"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Random weights multiplied by a tiny factor (e.g., 0.01)"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# BAD - Common mistake\nW = np.random.randn(100, 128) * 0.01  # Too small!"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "What happens"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Vanishing gradients"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Gradients become tiny → weights barely update\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Signal loss"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Activations diminish as they propagate through layers\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Slow convergence"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Network learns extremely slowly.md)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Why it's bad"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":\n- For deep networks: small weights × small weights ×... → exponentially small\n- Gradients shrink as they move backward → early layers train very slowly or not at all\n- Model doesn't reach optimum in training time"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Result"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Training takes forever or never reaches good performance."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Pitfall 4: ❌ Very Large Random Values"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "What"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Random weights in large range (e.g., 0 to 1, or std=10)"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# BAD - Common mistake\nW = np.random.randn(100, 128) * 10  # Too large!"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "What happens"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Exploding gradients"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Gradients grow too large → unstable updates\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Saturation"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Activations saturate activation functions (sigmoid/tanh → gradient ≈ 0).md)\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "NaN values"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Weight swings cause overflow → "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "NaN"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (Not a Number)\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Divergence"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Loss oscillates wildly or diverges.md)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Why it's bad"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":\n- Large weights × large weights ×... → exponentially large ("}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "10^{6} \\cdot 10^{6} \\cdot 10^{6} = 10^{18}"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ")\n- Can't reach optimum (requires small steps, not large swings)\n- Activation saturation → vanishing gradient despite large weights.md)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Result"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Training is unstable, loss diverges, or model crashes with NaN."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Summary Table: What Goes Wrong"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Pitfall"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Weight Range"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Primary Problem"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Secondary Problem"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Outcome"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Zero"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "All 0"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Identical gradients"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Symmetry"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "No learning"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (linear model)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Constant"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "All same (e.g., 0.5)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Identical gradients"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Symmetry"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "No diversity"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (single neuron)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Too small"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "~0.01 × random"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Vanishing gradients"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Signal loss"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Slow/failed learning"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Too large"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "~10 × random"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Exploding gradients"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Saturation"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Unstable/divergent"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The Three Serious Problems from Bad Initialization"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "When initialization numbers are chosen wrongly, networks suffer from:"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Problem"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Cause"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Effect"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Vanishing Gradients"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Weights too small"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Learning signal too weak → weights stop updating"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Exploding Gradients"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Weights too large"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Learning signal too large → unstable updates"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Slow Convergence"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Weights too small/symmetric"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Network learns extremely slowly"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Why These Pitfalls Happen"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "1. Symmetry Breaking Failure"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Concept"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Neurons need to start differently to learn different features."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Problem"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Zero/constant initialization → all neurons identical → identical updates → never diversify."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Solution"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Random initialization"}, {"type": "text", "text": " breaks symmetry."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "2. Scale Mismatch"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Concept"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Weights need to be scaled to match the number of inputs."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Problem"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": - Small weights: signal diminishes through layers\n- Large weights: signal explodes through layers"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Solution"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Scaled initialization"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (Xavier/He)."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "3. Activation Function Ignorance"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Concept"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Different activations need different scales."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Problem"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Using Xavier (for sigmoid/tanh) with ReLU → vanishing variance."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Solution"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Match initialization to activation:\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Sigmoid/tanh"}, {"type": "text", "text": " → "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Xavier"}, {"type": "text", "text": "\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "ReLU"}, {"type": "text", "text": " → "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "He"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "How to Avoid These Pitfalls"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "✅ Best Practices"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Practice"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Why"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Use Xavier initialization"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Scaled random for sigmoid/tanh"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Use He initialization"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Scaled random for ReLU"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Never initialize to zero"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Symmetry never breaks"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Never initialize to constant"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Same as zero"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Avoid small random (×0.01)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Vanishing gradients"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Avoid large random (×10)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Exploding gradients"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Match init to activation"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Xavier for sigmoid/tanh, He for ReLU"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "✅ Correct Code Examples"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# GOOD - He initialization for ReLU\nimport torch.nn.init as init\ninit.kaiming_normal_(layer.weight)  # PyTorch\n\n# GOOD - Xavier initialization for tanh\ninit.xavier_normal_(layer.weight)  # PyTorch\n\n# GOOD - TensorFlow/Keras\nfrom tensorflow.keras.initializers import HeNormal(), GlorotUniform()\nlayer = tf.keras.layers.Dense(128, kernel_initializer=HeNormal(), activation='relu')"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key Takeaways"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Zero initialization"}, {"type": "text", "text": " → network becomes linear model, "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "no learning"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Constant initialization"}, {"type": "text", "text": " → same problem as zero, "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "no diversity"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Small random"}, {"type": "text", "text": " → "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "vanishing gradients"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", slow learning.md)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Large random"}, {"type": "text", "text": " → "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "exploding gradients"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", unstable/divergent"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "All pitfalls"}, {"type": "text", "text": " stem from: symmetry failure, scale mismatch, activation mismatch"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Solution"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Use "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "scaled random initialization"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (Xavier/He) matched to activation function"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Proper initialization is critical"}, {"type": "text", "text": " for deep learning stability — poor initialization makes networks un-trainable from iteration 1"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The deep learning community considers zero/constant initialization "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "poor practice"}, {"type": "text", "text": " — it's a fundamental mistake that breaks training entirely."}]}]}}